Let $x_1$ be the $x$-coordinate of the centroid of $R$.
Let $x_2$ be the $x$-coordinate of the centroid of the solid generated by rotating $R$ about the $x$-axis.
Prove that $x_1 < x_2$.
-/
theorem putnam_2025_b2
